{"tid":2112341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有屯門區議員稱寄工作報告被香港郵政拒絕　斥政治審查","createTime":"2020-07-17T08:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T09:41:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d9da4fc010d8a657ef128f53744812f834c743","tid":2112341,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538362-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538362-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fb566cd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538362-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=383f96a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538362-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨屯門區議員馬旗表示，香港郵政拒絕郵寄他的區議會工作報告，沒有說明原因，他批評做法是政治審查，會向申訴專員公署投訴。<br />\n<br />\n馬旗表示，本月2日已在網上申請投寄，因一星期尚未完成審批，向職員詢問原因，對方口頭表示與報告內的部分內容有關。他說，香港郵政在本月10日批准投寄，但翌日又指郵件內容正在審閱中，最後拒絕投寄申請，但沒有說明原因。<br />\n<br />\n馬旗又說香港郵政一度拒絕將4700份工作報告發還，最後答應在剪去右上角「通函郵寄」後會交還所有工作報告。"},{"pid":"a8ae489e9e106deb31bc0fd1de3bc021a610f7d8","tid":2112341,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T08:51:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9516e264eb899e659b9c1d2d2741642f92bb8de","tid":2112341,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bc70d1f1edcba327a84660c4d666e6826a5e3d7a","tid":2112341,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:15:18.000Z","msg":"入得美國制裁名單 認真"},{"pid":"45c6a78d28e141808842e3c9d3d423920e98d3e7","tid":2112341,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}